Class LexicalAnalysis<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.myorb.math.expressions.tree.LexicalAnalysis<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of values from expressions

    public class LexicalAnalysis<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    locate parenthetical sub-expressions in token sequence. replace found sequences with sub-expression node structure.

    Michael Druckman
